Version Control
 is a system that allow us to  have multiple vergions of the same project every one is diffrent from anther that helps us heep the changes in a history that can help  us if we 
 want to get back to the pervious step
 using this system  minmmize data lose.
 ## Centralized Version Control
before this system if their is a team that is working on a project and they are work in the same code every one of them have his own copy and 
 but now they all can use  this system and work on the same copy and share it with each other.
 
  their is  anther tyoe of  version control and its the Distributed version control.
